<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{buyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Great news! Your prequalification for the mortgage on <strong>{{propertyName}}</strong> has been approved.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Your Provisional Offer Letter is now ready for your review. This letter outlines the preliminary terms of your mortgage, including:
</p>

<ul style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; padding-left:20px;">
    <li>Approved loan amount: <strong>{{loanAmount}}</strong></li>
    <li>Interest rate: <strong>{{interestRate}}%</strong></li>
    <li>Loan term: <strong>{{loanTerm}}</strong></li>
    <li>Estimated monthly payment: <strong>{{monthlyPayment}}</strong></li>
</ul>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Please review the offer letter carefully. If you agree to the terms, you can proceed to sign the document electronically.
</p>

{{#if signatureUrl}}
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:30px 0;">
    <tr>
        <td align="center">
            <a href="{{signatureUrl}}" style="background-color:#2563EB; color:#ffffff; padding:14px 28px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; display:inline-block;">
                Review & Sign Offer Letter
            </a>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
{{/if}}

{{#if expiryDate}}
<p style="font-size:12px; line-height:20px; color:#6B7280; margin:20px 0;">
    This offer is valid until <strong>{{expiryDate}}</strong>. After this date, you may need to reapply for prequalification.
</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    If you have any questions about the terms or need clarification, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0 10px 0;">
